Use this method to receive the results of a RAW format capture. (If you request capture in both RAW and a processed format, the photo output calls both this method and the
method.)
You must implement either this method or the
method if you request capture in a RAW format. The photo output validates this requirement when you call its
method; if your delegate does not implement the correct methods, the photo output raises an exception.

If you request RAW format capture, the photo output calls this method once for each exposure in the capture request. If you request a single image capture, this method is called once. If you request a bracketed capture with multiple exposures, this method is called once for each exposure.
